    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Vue InstantSearch v3 is using InstantSearch v4 under the hood, this means that you have access to initialUiState. However the function `onStateChange` has not been added as a parameter yet. Is this something you're still interested in now? ",
